108
00:16:50,520 --> 00:16:54,420
Love... is tiring.

109
00:16:55,700 --> 00:17:00,220
I used to think that if there were a next life,

110
00:17:01,300 --> 00:17:05,140
I must find her and give her happiness.

111
00:17:06,800 --> 00:17:08,860
But I found out

112
00:17:10,440 --> 00:17:13,080
that even if I can relive my life,

113
00:17:13,890 --> 00:17:16,160
