193
00:28:52,010 --> 00:28:54,300
How does she become like this today?

194
00:28:54,300 --> 00:28:57,790
It's my fault. Please forgive me, Your Imperial Highness.

195
00:28:57,790 --> 00:29:00,220
Get the physicians.

196
00:29:19,110 --> 00:29:23,080
Empress, the coldness has infiltrated the crown princess consort' body.

197
00:29:23,080 --> 00:29:26,120
She was out in the cold for a long time, combined with mental stress,

198
00:29:26,120 --> 00:29:28,200
so she fell ill.

199
00:29:28,200 --> 00:29:30,280
She will need time to recuperate.

200
00:29:30,280 --> 00:29:32,910
Long time in the cold?

201
00:29:33,900 --> 00:29:37,180
Wasn't she with the crown prince yesterday?

202
00:29:41,180 --> 00:29:45,510
Crown Prince, tell me what happened.

203
00:29:45,510 --> 00:29:48,320
Last night, I went to Qingluan Hall.

204
00:29:48,320 --> 00:29:51,480
I don't know how she caught a cold.

205
00:29:51,480 --> 00:29:53,990
You and the crown princess consort's wedding was yesterday.

206
00:29:53,990 --> 00:29:56,700
And you stayed the night at Qingluan Hall?

207
00:29:56,700 --> 00:29:58,810
It's a breach in etiquette.

208
00:29:59,480 --> 00:30:03,100
I go wherever I want to go, as long as it's not her place.

209
00:30:03,100 --> 00:30:04,900
Nonsense!

210
00:30:06,240 --> 00:30:07,930
- Wei Chen.
- I'm here.

211
00:30:07,930 --> 00:30:09,490
Announce my edict.

212
00:30:09,490 --> 00:30:12,370
Related Lady of Excellence for Zhao seduced His Highness and forgot her place.

213
00:30:12,370 --> 00:30:14,360
She is to be locked in Qingluan Hall for half a month.

214
00:30:14,360 --> 00:30:18,170
No one may visit her, including the crown prince.

215
00:30:18,170 --> 00:30:21,690
Imperial Mother, this has nothing to do with Sese.

216
00:30:23,990 --> 00:30:26,670
You think I am wrong to punish her?

217
00:30:34,700 --> 00:30:37,580
It's fine that you discard the rules and traditions,

218
00:30:37,580 --> 00:30:41,550
but Zhao Sese should know the palace rules.

219
00:30:41,550 --> 00:30:44,560
She not only did not stop you, but she also allowed you to stay in her place.

220
00:30:44,560 --> 00:30:47,220
She is confusing the lord.

221
00:30:49,150 --> 00:30:51,450
If you think I'm wrong,

222
00:30:51,450 --> 00:30:54,610
you can ask the Ancestral Court to give a judgment.

223
00:30:54,610 --> 00:30:55,840
I...

224
00:30:55,840 --> 00:30:58,550
If it comes to that,

225
00:30:58,550 --> 00:31:01,370
it may be more than half a month of house arrest.

226
00:31:03,670 --> 00:31:07,790
I am sorry, Imperial Mother. I was wrong.

227
00:31:32,560 --> 00:31:34,890
Your Highness.

228
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:39,540
A'Du.

229
00:31:40,550 --> 00:31:42,260
It's okay.

230
00:31:45,500 --> 00:31:46,740
