248
00:33:56,430 --> 00:34:00,210
Related Lady of Excellence for Zhao seduced the lord and forget her status.

249
00:34:00,210 --> 00:34:02,780
She is to be locked in Qingluan Hall for half a month.

250
00:34:02,780 --> 00:34:05,280
