It was the crown prince who came here himself,

253
00:34:24,860 --> 00:34:27,130
why is our lady being punished?

254
00:34:27,130 --> 00:34:30,510
Jin'er, you must never say such a thing.

255
00:34:33,160 --> 00:34:36,060
The empress never liked me.

256
00:34:36,060 --> 00:34:39,350
She always looked for opportunities to oppress me.

257
00:34:39,350 --> 00:34:41,740
What she doesn't know is the more she oppresses me,

258
00:34:41,740 --> 00:34:44,960
the more Crown Prince will feel for me.

259
00:34:44,960 --> 00:34:48,940
In the Eastern Palace, as long as the crown prince cares about me,

260
00:34:48,940 --> 00:34:50,980
I'm happy.

261
00:35:11,960 --> 00:35:13,440
Your Highness.

262
00:35:13,440 --> 00:35:17,760
How is her illness?

263
00:35:17,760 --> 00:35:20,040
Crown Princess Consort is gravely ill this time.

264
00:35:20,040 --> 00:35:22,100
She needs to recuperate for a few days.

265
00:35:23,200 --> 00:35:29,050
Your Highness, are you really not going to let the Palace Pharmaceutical Service treat the crown princess consort?

266
00:35:30,150 --> 00:35:32,180
Sese has been put on house arrest.

267
00:35:32,180 --> 00:35:35,750
If I don't pretend to be angry,

268
00:35:35,750 --> 00:35:38,320
she might become suspicious.

269
00:35:38,850 --> 00:35:43,720
But the crown princess consort's illness can't be left untreated.

270
00:35:43,720 --> 00:35:45,520
I know.

271
00:35:46,210 --> 00:35:51,020
But every item in the Eastern Palace is recorded.

272
00:35:52,830 --> 00:35:58,760
So, I would like you to bring some good medication from your home.

273
00:36:00,630 --> 00:36:01,930
Oh right!

274
00:36:01,930 --> 00:36:05,920
That Yongniang by her side is Imperial Great-Grandmother's servant. She's very trustworthy.

275
00:36:05,920 --> 00:36:08,790
You go give her the medicine secretly.

276
00:36:08,790 --> 00:36:10,750
Don't let anyone find out.

277
00:36:13,800 --> 00:36:18,420
Also, take this chance to investigate

278
00:36:18,420 --> 00:36:23,750
how many people in the Eastern Palace are spies for Prime Minister Gao and the empress.

279
00:36:23,750 --> 00:36:25,300
Yes.

280
00:36:35,820 --> 00:36:37,890
Take good care of the crown princess consort.

281
00:36:38,480 --> 00:36:40,150
Thank you, General Pei, for your help.

282
00:36:40,150 --> 00:36:43,760
If it weren't for your help, I wouldn't know what to do.

283
00:36:43,760 --> 00:36:46,730
All right. Hurry up and brew the medication for her.

284
00:36:46,730 --> 00:36:48,220
Yes.

285
00:37:02,830 --> 00:37:07,250
Crown Prince knows that Prime Minister Gao wants him to be someone who doesn't care about the government

286
00:37:07,250 --> 00:37:09,610
and only care about love.

287
00:37:09,610 --> 00:37:12,180
This way, he will be able to control the government.

288
00:37:12,180 --> 00:37:15,300
In the Eastern Palace now, there are many spies for Prime Minister Gao.

289
00:37:15,300 --> 00:37:17,010
The crown prince wants to use this opportunity to

290
00:37:17,010 --> 00:37:20,010
hide his talent, bide his time, and control the situation secretly.

291
00:37:21,950 --> 00:37:25,900
Please tell the crown prince that I've asked Jian'er

292
00:37:25,900 --> 00:37:29,420
to gather all the nearby Submerged Dragon Envoys to the capital.

293
00:37:29,420 --> 00:37:33,260
We have spies in Gao Manor and Ye Manor.

294
00:37:33,260 --> 00:37:36,490
I've replaced all the Eastern Palace guards with my people.

295
00:37:36,490 --> 00:37:41,270
But to avoid any suspicions from Prime Minister Gao, we couldn't get rid of all the eunuchs and ladies-in-waiting.

296
00:37:41,270 --> 00:37:43,010
You should leave some.

297
00:37:43,010 --> 00:37:47,320
If you get rid of all of them, you are more like to give yourself away.

298
00:37:47,320 --> 00:37:49,120
Oh right!

299
00:37:49,120 --> 00:37:53,960
Among those three preceptors of His Highness, is that Fang Shiqing working for Prime Minister Gao?

300
00:37:53,960 --> 00:37:55,600
The crown prince already knows about this.

301
00:37:55,600 --> 00:37:59,710
He wants to use Fang Shiqing as a pawn in his performance.

302
00:37:59,710 --> 00:38:01,480
Oh right, Sir Chai.

303
00:38:01,480 --> 00:38:04,830
His Highness said that since he is living in the Eastern Palace now,

304
00:38:04,830 --> 00:38:09,490
it's inconvenient for him to go out. He wanted me to tell you to take good care of yourself.

305
00:38:12,650 --> 00:38:14,860
Oh right, General Pei.

306
00:38:14,860 --> 00:38:17,850
You have to be more cautious.

307
00:38:18,740 --> 00:38:20,400
I don't know why,

308
00:38:20,400 --> 00:38:25,180
but I think the crown prince's attitude toward the ninth princess is different.

309
00:38:26,510 --> 00:38:28,420
The crown prince has just secured his position.

310
00:38:28,420 --> 00:38:31,150
He can't make any mistakes now.

311
00:38:32,350 --> 00:38:33,990
You make sure to keep an eye on things.

312
00:38:33,990 --> 00:38:37,470
If there are any abnormalities, contact me immediately.

313
00:38:37,470 --> 00:38:40,050
Don't worry, Sir Chai.

314
00:38:41,240 --> 00:38:44,000
A'Du, help the crown princess consort up.

315
00:39:03,300 --> 00:39:05,030
Handkerchief.

316
00:39:09,820 --> 00:39:12,710
Your Highness, it took a lot of effort to find this medication.

317
00:39:12,710 --> 00:39:15,100
Make sure you drink it all.

318
00:39:33,310 --> 00:39:35,600
Your Highness, have a bit of this.

319
00:39:35,600 --> 00:39:37,820
Here, I'll feed you.

320
00:39:38,480 --> 00:39:39,920
I don't want to eat.

321
00:39:39,920 --> 00:39:42,770
The medicine won't help you as much as food. Just take one bite.

322
00:39:42,770 --> 00:39:45,500
Just eat one bite. I'll feed you.

323
00:39:45,500 --> 00:39:49,440
I'm tired. You go rest, too.

324
00:40:26,160 --> 00:40:27,860
Why are you here again?

325
00:40:27,860 --> 00:40:30,880
Of course, I came to bring food for a foodie like you.

326
00:40:39,790 --> 00:40:41,850
Lamb ribs!

327
00:40:41,850 --> 00:40:44,650
Didn't you say that sick people can't eat lamb ribs?

328
00:40:44,650 --> 00:40:47,190
You would only bring me some meat broth.

329
00:40:47,190 --> 00:40:49,110
You already drank meat broth for a few days.

330
00:40:49,110 --> 00:40:51,110
You are almost fully recovered,

331
00:40:51,110 --> 00:40:53,220
but still don't have any strength.

332
00:40:55,340 --> 00:40:58,470
I want to drink grape wine.

333
00:40:58,470 --> 00:41:01,970
I knew it. I brought some for you.

334
00:41:14,280 --> 00:41:18,420
I also want to eat chilled grapes with frost.

335
00:41:20,680 --> 00:41:23,930
I'll have someone bring some to you in a few days.

336
00:41:28,940 --> 00:41:31,000
Gu Jian, tell me.

337
00:41:31,000 --> 00:41:35,590
When will my dad reply to my letters?

338
00:41:35,590 --> 00:41:38,820
