339
00:41:41,610 --> 00:41:46,340
From here to the Xi State, the travel time is three months. Wait a little longer.

340
00:41:47,560 --> 00:41:49,910
But I miss home.

341
00:41:50,510 --> 00:41:55,610
I miss my parents. I also miss Xi State.

342
00:42:01,350 --> 00:42:06,950
[Eastern Palace]

343
00:42:15,460 --> 00:42:16,950
Who's there?

344
00:42:19,720 --> 00:42:21,310
Cousin?

345
00:42:21,880 --> 00:42:23,840
No one saw you, right?

346
00:42:27,610 --> 00:42:29,460
Why did you come to see me?

347
00:42:29,460 --> 00:42:32,040
During your wedding with the crown princess consort,

348
00:42:32,040 --> 00:42:35,240
