349
00:42:35,240 --> 00:42:36,770
Yes.

350
00:42:36,770 --> 00:42:39,550
Could you pick some out to gift to Xiaofeng?

351
00:42:39,550 --> 00:42:42,400
Just say that her family sent them to her.

352
00:42:48,560 --> 00:42:52,900
Also, tell her that this letter was written by her royal father.

353
00:42:57,790 --> 00:42:59,790
