354
00:42:59,790 --> 00:43:03,810
She still doesn't know that her mother is dead.

355
00:43:03,810 --> 00:43:07,270
She has been sending one letter after another home.

356
00:43:07,270 --> 00:43:10,720
She's alone in the palace and there's no one to take care of her.

357
00:43:10,720 --> 00:43:15,760
Now that she's your wife, the only person she can trust is you.

